    exposed a PRODUCTION gap: an origin path not byte-equal to a registry entry made a
    pending gate VANISH from the merged digest. Fixed by construction, not by assert:
    TG_ROOT normalized in lib.sh, --workspace normalized in send-event.sh, orphan-origin
    pending gates surface in the primary digest section; harness normalizes $SB too.
  head run 2: 20/21. FAIL 20 = harness assertion oversight (registry holds THREE
